1. Installation

  # apt-get install unixodbc
  # cp config/odbcinst.ini /etc/odbcinst.ini
 


2. Drivers

  Oracle ODBC connector (Linux):
   - http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/topics/linuxx86-64soft-092277.html

  Oracle ODBC connector (Windows):
   - http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/database/windows/downloads/index-096177.html

  MySQL ODBC connector (Debian):
   - apt-get install mysql-connector-odbc

  FreeTDS ODBC connector (Debian):
   - apt-get install tdsodbc

  PostgreSQL ODBC connector (Debian):
   - apt-get install odbc-postgresql



3. Extras

  # apt-get install python-pyodbc



4. Examples

  Check example/ directory.


